---
title: Pantry Agent – Sequence Diagram
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant App as Client App
    participant Graph as LangGraph
    participant MM as Memory Store
    participant LLM as OpenAI GPT-4o
    participant API as Pantry REST API

    User->>App: "Scan my fridge photo" + image.jpg
    App->>Graph: invoke(state, config={thread_id, user_id})

    activate Graph
    Graph->>MM: load_user_memory(user_id)
    MM-->>Graph: {dietary_prefs, allergies, ...}

    Graph->>LLM: classify_intent(user_message)
    LLM-->>Graph: {intent: "scan_groceries", domain: "Vision", has_image: true}

    Graph->>LLM: agent_node(messages + tools + system_prompt)
    LLM-->>Graph: tool_call: extract_ingredients_from_image(image_data=..., auto_save=true)

    Graph->>API: POST /api/ai/vision/extract-save
    API-->>Graph: {extracted_items: [...], confidence: 0.72, saved: false}

    Graph->>LLM: agent_node(messages including ToolMessage)
    LLM-->>Graph: "I found 8 ingredients with 72% confidence. Please review."

    Graph->>Graph: validate_output → confidence=0.72 < 0.80 → approval_required=true

    Graph-->>App: interrupt({reason: "Low confidence", items: [...]})
    deactivate Graph

    App->>User: "Please review these 8 items before saving"
    User->>App: "Approved – save all"
    App->>Graph: Command(resume={approved: true})

    activate Graph
    Graph->>API: POST /api/pantry (for each item)
    API-->>Graph: 200 OK × 8

    Graph->>LLM: update_memory(conversation_summary)
    LLM-->>Graph: {preferences_learned: [], pantry_changes: ["added spinach", ...]}
    Graph->>MM: save_user_memory(user_id, updated_memory)

    Graph-->>App: final state {messages: [...], pantry_items: [...]}
    deactivate Graph

    App->>User: "✅ Saved 8 ingredients to your pantry!"

    Note over User,API: ── Follow-up turn ──

    User->>App: "What can I cook with these?"
    App->>Graph: invoke(state, config={thread_id})   ← same thread_id, memory loaded

    activate Graph
    Graph->>MM: load_user_memory(user_id)
    Graph->>LLM: classify_intent → domain=Recipes
    Graph->>LLM: agent_node → tool_call: recommend_recipes()
    Graph->>API: GET /api/ai/recipes
    API-->>Graph: {recipes: [{name: "Spinach Omelette", ...}, ...]}
    Graph->>LLM: agent_node → "Here are 5 recipes you can make right now!"
    Graph->>Graph: validate_output → no issues → update_memory → END
    Graph-->>App: {messages: [...], recipes: [...]}
    deactivate Graph

    App->>User: "Here are 5 recipes you can cook right now! 🍳"
